    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for libzip</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">Libzip was updated to fix one security issue.

A zip file with an unusually large number of entries could have caused an integer overflow leading to a write past the heap boundary, crashing the application. (CVE-2015-2331 bnc#923240)
</Note>
